name: Pink Gerbera Invitation
description:
Luxurious handmade photographic wedding invitation.  
'Wedding Invitation' is foil embossed on the front.  'Evening Invitation' is available also for evening reception guests.

Card Includes matching envelope, RSVP card and envelope.  Card shown is 'Cotton White'. 
RSVP reply envelope will be printed with your chosen reply address.

All images are exclusive of Suzy Q Cards and 100% original.
'Traditional' wording has been used inside, please see 'ordering options' for details
